From rgentlem at fhcrc.org  Sun Sep 23 17:00:35 2007
From: rgentlem at fhcrc.org (Robert Gentleman)
Date: Sun, 23 Sep 2007 08:00:35 -0700
Subject: [Bioc-devel] Requirment for a Vignette
In-Reply-To: <46F6075D.5030005@jimmy.harvard.edu>
